name: Sunny
description:
The Lovely Kittens is a collection of 100 unique vector illustrations hand drawn well-designed Kittens united together to get on Tezos Blockchain. 

Adopt a stray cat, open your heart to a homeless cat.
We support a few individual shelter who does rescue cats with the sales profit of this collection. To see the cats story visit @6lovely.cats on Instagram.
